---
import ServiceLayout from '../../components/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Outdoor Therapy"
  description="Nature-based occupational therapy in Pakenham. Outdoor therapeutic interventions that harness the healing power of nature for children, youth and families."
  image="/images/services/outdoor-therapy.jpg"
>
  <h2>Nature as a Therapeutic Tool</h2>
  <p>At Adventure Therapy Services, we believe that nature isn't just a backdrop — it is a powerful tool for regulation, skill building, and personal growth. Our outdoor therapy sessions take place in natural environments where participants can connect with the land, animals, and each other.</p>

  <p>Research shows that spending time in nature reduces stress, improves mood, and enhances cognitive function. Our outdoor therapy program combines these benefits with evidence-based occupational therapy interventions.</p>

  <h2>What We Offer</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Nature-based therapeutic activities tailored to individual goals</li>
    <li>Sensory exploration and regulation in outdoor settings</li>
    <li>Bushwalking and nature connection experiences</li>
    <li>Gardening and land-based activities</li>
    <li>Animal-assisted interactions in natural environments</li>
    <li>Social skills development through group outdoor activities</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Who Can Benefit?</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Children and young people who thrive in outdoor environments</li>
    <li>Individuals seeking alternatives to clinic-based therapy</li>
    <li>People who benefit from sensory-rich, natural environments</li>
    <li>Anyone looking to build confidence, resilience, and independence</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>What to Expect</h2>
  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-number">1</div>
      <div>
        <h3>Getting Started</h3>
        <p>We begin with an initial consultation to understand your goals and determine how outdoor therapy can best support you. Sessions take place at our property at 309 Army Road, Pakenham.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-number">2</div>
      <div>
        <h3>Tailored Sessions</h3>
        <p>Each session is designed around your individual therapeutic goals, using the natural environment as a dynamic, engaging setting for skill development and growth.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-number">3</div>
      <div>
        <h3>Building Skills for Life</h3>
        <p>Our outdoor therapy program is designed to build transferable skills — confidence, regulation, social connection, and independence — that carry over into everyday life.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p>Please check our <a href="/faqs/">frequently asked questions</a> page for information on our fees & charges and anything you're unsure of.</p>
</ServiceLayout>
